title: New Jersey Midterm Elections: What to Know About Key Races
description: Election Day is Tuesday, Nov. 8. Registered voters can also cast ballots early, on machines, this weekend.
dc:creator: Tracey Tully
media:credit: Dave Sanders for The New York Times
media:description: The most hotly contested race in New Jersey is between Representative Tom Malinowski, right, a Democrat, and his Republican challenger, Tom Kean Jr.
